The '''Ottethan Empire''' was located in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]]. It contained twelve [[Star system/Legends|systems]], of which the [[Ottethan system/Legends|Ottethan system]] was the capital. It was ruled by a [[Ottethan warlord|warlord]] whom grew tired of his lover, [[Neema-Da-Boda]], and fed her to [[Rancor/Legends|rancors]]. [[Vima-Da-Boda]] killed him in revenge [[31 BBY/Legends|31 BBY]].

